    <!-- GREEK not showing ^^^ -->
                  <item n="4" xml:id="addition4"><locus from="36a" to="36a"/><ref target="#a1"/>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܘܕܒ̈ܠܐ. ܘܩܪ̈ܬܠܘܬܐ ܕܥ̈ܢܒܐ</quote>(1 Chron. xii. 40),<label>marg.</label><quote xml:lang="syr">ܥ̈ܠܘܗܝ ܕܚܡܪܐ ܐܝܟ ܡܫܠܡܢܘܬܐ ܕܥܒܪ̈ܝܐ</quote> and <quote xml:lang="syr">ܪ̈ܠܝܬܐ ܕܥ̈ܢܒܐ </quote></item>
